data.title: Raja Nazrin dimasyhurkan sebagai Sultan Perak yang baru
data.meta_description:
Raja Nazrin Shah ibni Almarhum Sultan Azlan Shah ditabalkan sebagai Sultan Perak Darul Ridhwan yang ke-35 tepat jam 3.15 petang ini yang membawa kepada gelaran Paduka Seri Sultan Nazrin.

	Pengumuman pelantikan itu diumumkan oleh Orang Kaya Bendahara Seri Maharaja Jen (Bersara) Tan Sri Mohd Zainuddin di sebelah jenazah Almarhum Sultan Azlan Shah...

Associated Press

Woman from India disappears down a sinkhole in Malaysia's capital

A woman from India disappeared in Malaysia’s capital Friday when pavement collapsed beneath her and she fell into a sinkhole where she may have been swept away by an underground water current, police said. The woman plunged into the 8-meter-deep (26-foot-deep) sinkhole in the Dang Wangi area of the Malaysian capital, where local police chief Sulizmie Affendy Sulaiman said witnesses saw the paved walkway suddenly collapse under her while she was walking. The woman was identified as a 48-year-old tourist from India.

Lee’s prominence: Lee Hsien Loong, who served two decades as prime minister, is respected in Singapore for his pragmatic leadership.

Russian ambassador to U.S. says Putin has plan of action for Kursk incursion

"I tell you sincerely that the president has made a decision," the TASS state news agency quoted Antonov as saying late on Thursday. "I am firmly convinced that everyone will be severely punished for what has happened in Kursk region." The comments by Antonov, who did not provide further details on Putin's plans, came after the Kremlin leader held a meeting on Thursday with senior officials, including the governors of border regions, over two weeks after Ukraine launched its lightning attack, the biggest incursion into Russia by a foreign power since World War Two.
